tancy. The company serves various verticals comprising banking and financials, healthcare and life sciences, supply chain and logistics, energy, education, environment, and other industries. The company was formerly known as KLK Electrical Limited and changed its name to Edvenswa Enterprises Limited in November 2022. Edvenswa Enterprises Limited was incorporated in 1980 and is based in Hyderabad, India."}}